I will display this model publicly for academic research and discussion. I hope to discuss working methods with you. I strongly advise against uploading any NSFW generated by this model. You are warmly welcome to communicate with me here on how to improve the working method and make the model more realistic. If you have any suggestions, such as choosing a different base model, training with more images, increasing the number of training steps, or changing the training size for a more realistic overall effect, please feel free to leave a comment below.

如本lora侵犯了您的权利，请联系我，将会下架处理。
